{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to '<strong>Restaurats</strong>' - a unique tavern simulator where you are not just a waiter, but an entire team of professional rats! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Your mission?</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To become the coolest rats in the restaurant business. Get ready for culinary battles: from cooking mushroom soup to mixing cocktails like &quot;<i>Honey Sucker</i>&quot;. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>But that's not all! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gather around a team of up to 4 players and impress guests with not only delicious dishes but also impeccable service. After all, who knows hospitality better than rats?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And <strong>remember</strong>, every satisfied customer is a step towards expanding your rat kingdom. So forward, rat monarchs, it's time to conquer culinary heights together! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Cooking</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870920/extras/run.png?t=1731231293\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870920/extras/cook616.gif?t=1731231293\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cook dishes following the recipes you study. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The more complex the recipe - the more bonuses you will receive.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Customer service</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870920/extras/run.png?t=1731231293\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870920/extras/serv616.gif?t=1731231293\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Serving restaurant customers: Escort them to their tables, take their orders, cook the dishes they have ordered and then serve them to your guests. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The visitors are represented by different creatures, each with their own preferences and requirements. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You must take into account the preferences and relationships between the creatures when seating the respective customers at the tables.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Character improvement</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870920/extras/run.png?t=1731231293\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Level up your character by gaining experience and improving your skills. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Change the appearance of your characters.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Cards</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870920/extras/run.png?t=1731231293\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870920/extras/card616.gif?t=1731231293\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Special cards that you can receive at the end of each working day. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cards can be related to various dishes, special abilities, or money and reputation. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use cards to improve your restaurant or get additional bonuses.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Improving the restaurant</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870920/extras/run.png?t=1731231293\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870920/extras/build616.gif?t=1731231293\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Improve your restaurant.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Buy new blueprints and install them in the restaurant to improve its functionality and attractiveness for visitors. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Expand the restaurant to accommodate more visitors.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Tax on the restaurant</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870920/extras/run.png?t=1731231293\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870920/extras/tax616.gif?t=1731231293\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Don't forget to pay the tax every day to maintain the restaurant's operation.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>VIP Visitors</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2870920/extras/run.png?t=1731231293\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unique characters of existing creatures.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">They can come into the restaurant at any time and cause various troubles for the players. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">However, if you fulfill their requirements, you will receive additional bonuses.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Events</strong></p><p class=\"bb_pa